Description: A fun 5K Run/Walk in support of local scholarships and student mentoring programs.  The ALGA (Alexandria Leigh Goodwin Angel) Foundation, celebrates Joy, random acts of kindness and the love of life just as Alex did.  With her unexpected passing, Alex left a hole in the world.  The work of the ALGA Foundation continues her legacy of love.  The 5K course, with the start and finish on Parkview Ave near Clifton Ave, will loop through the neighborhood at Jeffrey Park.  This event will be chip timed.
